how do you want to do this part?

775
00:50:01,790 --> 00:50:03,690
If you have any suggestions,
I'll follow it.

776
00:50:03,690 --> 00:50:05,610
- Really? Okay.
- Yes.

777
00:50:12,500 --> 00:50:13,510
Mr. Kwon.

778
00:50:14,770 --> 00:50:15,780
Hi.

779
00:50:17,380 --> 00:50:18,690
What brings you here?

780
00:50:19,270 --> 00:50:21,160
I had some business at court.

781
00:50:21,340 --> 00:50:24,240
I heard you're shooting and
came in case you need any help.

782
00:50:26,840 --> 00:50:28,760
I'm so glad I'm shooting
in front of the court.

783
00:50:28,920 --> 00:50:30,730
We got to bump into each other like this.

784
00:50:30,980 --> 00:50:33,310
- Yes.
- Yun Seo, it's time to shoot.

785
00:50:36,900 --> 00:50:37,910
