859
00:55:16,370 --> 00:55:18,870
You can each go buy some spring outfits.

860
00:55:19,410 --> 00:55:20,720
Thank you, Mr. Yeon.

861
00:55:20,780 --> 00:55:22,800
Why don't we buy a couple outfit?

862
00:55:22,940 --> 00:55:25,510
