perfect for your cute style.

863
00:55:26,750 --> 00:55:27,820
It's okay.

864
00:55:27,820 --> 00:55:29,880
Let's get something that will...

865
00:55:29,880 --> 00:55:32,580
look perfect on you,
something luxurious and chic.

866
00:55:33,420 --> 00:55:34,470
Let's eat.

867
00:55:35,620 --> 00:55:39,200
Why do I have to use my own money
and watch something like that?

868
00:55:40,090 --> 00:55:42,930
Anyway, if there are any more
hidden couples, tell me now.

869
00:55:42,930 --> 00:55:46,000
We should all go get a group
outfit while we're at it.

870
00:55:46,000 --> 00:55:48,600
I'm already struggling with my loan.
Another 7,000 dollars...

871
00:55:48,600 --> 00:55:50,290
added to my 700,000
won't make a difference.

872
00:55:51,470 --> 00:55:54,840
Hae Yeong, if it's okay with you,

873
00:55:54,940 --> 00:55:56,780
would you like to go get a
new spring dress with me...

874
00:55:56,780 --> 00:55:57,990
I have many dresses.

875
00:56:10,490 --> 00:56:12,050
Mr. Kwon.

876
00:56:12,560 --> 00:56:14,350
Is something wrong?

877
00:56:15,930 --> 00:56:17,010
I know.

878
00:56:17,570 --> 00:56:19,590
Your face looks so grim today.

879
00:56:21,370 --> 00:56:24,010
Is it because you had a crush on Ms. Dan...

880
00:56:24,010 --> 00:56:26,640
and you feel heartbroken
since she's going out with Mr. Choi?

881
00:56:26,670 --> 00:56:27,990
Is that why you're drinking so much?

882
00:56:28,940 --> 00:56:30,090
Is that true?

883
00:56:30,850 --> 00:56:33,000
A crush is love too. I'll root for you.

884
00:56:33,580 --> 00:56:34,690
- Goodness.
- Oh, my.

885
00:56:42,860 --> 00:56:44,550
Mr. Kwon, are you still
at your company dinner?

886
00:56:46,960 --> 00:56:48,010
I see.

887
00:56:48,230 --> 00:56:50,420
I'm on my way home after today's shoot.

888
00:56:52,570 --> 00:56:54,890
Call me after dinner then.

889
00:56:56,140 --> 00:56:57,180
Okay.

890
00:56:58,870 --> 00:57:00,360
Did he say anything in particular?

891
00:57:00,470 --> 00:57:03,310
In particular? Like what?

892
00:57:03,410 --> 00:57:04,490
Well, it's just...

893
00:57:06,050 --> 00:57:07,570
It just seemed...

894
00:57:08,580 --> 00:57:11,550
he was jealous because of your kiss scene.

895
00:57:12,650 --> 00:57:15,690
I was just curious if he gave
you a hard time about it.

896
00:57:16,090 --> 00:57:17,130
What?

897
00:57:19,790 --> 00:57:21,880
That's the fate of the
boyfriend of a celebrity.

898
00:57:22,130 --> 00:57:24,730
He has to pretend he's okay
watching love scenes like that,

899
00:57:24,930 --> 00:57:26,720
but he feels jealous inside.

900
00:57:27,440 --> 00:57:30,140
He can't proudly tell anyone
that he's dating you either.

901
00:57:30,140 --> 00:57:32,870
And you can't even go to places
where there are a lot of people.

902
00:57:34,710 --> 00:57:35,750
Yun Seo.

903
00:57:36,880 --> 00:57:39,070
That's why I'm so worried...

904
00:57:39,680 --> 00:57:41,600
about the two of you dating.

905
00:57:42,250 --> 00:57:43,940
You can't help but get exhausted...

906
00:57:44,290 --> 00:57:46,270
when you're in a secret relationship.

907
00:57:54,760 --> 00:57:56,250
Here you go, honey.

908
00:57:59,830 --> 00:58:01,180
You too, honey.

909
00:58:03,870 --> 00:58:06,060
You guys are bringing so
much love to our firm.

910
00:58:07,510 --> 00:58:10,990
I'm not sure about that.
I'm starting to feel angry.

911
00:58:12,150 --> 00:58:14,780
Those two are slowly
helping me understand...

912
00:58:14,980 --> 00:58:17,680
why CEOs don't want their
employees to date each other.

913
00:58:17,950 --> 00:58:19,620
I mean, why would the CEO...

914
00:58:19,620 --> 00:58:21,710
want to pay people and
see them dating at the same time?

915
00:58:22,660 --> 00:58:24,950
I feel like I'll become
furious if I stay here.

916
00:58:25,030 --> 00:58:26,690
It seems like you're all done,
so let's go now.

917
00:58:26,690 --> 00:58:28,520
- Let's go.
- But I don't want to go.

918
00:58:29,300 --> 00:58:31,270
- Yun Seo!
- Hello.

919
00:58:31,270 --> 00:58:32,480
- Yun Seo.
- Yun Seo.

920
00:58:33,000 --> 00:58:34,450
What brings you here?

921
00:58:35,270 --> 00:58:39,080
I heard you guys are having a team
dinner here, so I dropped by.

922
00:58:39,410 --> 00:58:41,540
I'm glad you're here.
We were just getting started.

923
00:58:41,540 --> 00:58:42,720
Come this way.

924
00:58:44,450 --> 00:58:45,460
Sit here.

925
00:58:49,380 --> 00:58:50,560
Jong Hwa, where's your seat?

926
00:58:50,850 --> 00:58:52,840
- Over there, sir.
- Oh, I see. Okay.

927
00:58:56,160 --> 00:58:59,220
Yun Seo, we have big news.

928
00:58:59,330 --> 00:59:02,560
Apparently, Ms. Dan and
Mr. Choi are a couple now.

929
00:59:04,230 --> 00:59:06,390
- Really?
- Yes.

930
00:59:06,670 --> 00:59:09,630
I was actually going to tell you tomorrow.

931
00:59:11,140 --> 00:59:12,660
Congratulations.

932
00:59:12,740 --> 00:59:15,270
Jung Rok, aren't you glad to see Yun Seo?

933
00:59:15,410 --> 00:59:17,260
- Why aren't you saying anything?
- Pardon?

934
00:59:17,610 --> 00:59:20,950
Jung Rok, what's with you today?
Why do you look so down?

935
00:59:22,280 --> 00:59:23,390
Is it because it's spring?

936
00:59:23,680 --> 00:59:24,930
It must be because you feel lonely.

937
00:59:25,690 --> 00:59:26,930
- That must be it.
- That's nonsense.

938
00:59:27,420 --> 00:59:29,010
Don't lie to me.

939
00:59:29,060 --> 00:59:31,720
You know what? We should
set him up on a blind date.

940
00:59:33,630 --> 00:59:34,730
That's not necessary.

941
00:59:34,730 --> 00:59:37,100
Stop refusing the offer.
You're obviously single right now.

942
00:59:37,100 --> 00:59:39,250
You should do as I say
and go on a blind date.

943
00:59:40,030 --> 00:59:43,270
Ms. Kim, Ms. Dan, do you guys know anyone?

944
00:59:43,570 --> 00:59:44,720
- Do you know any single women?
- Anyone?

945
00:59:46,440 --> 00:59:47,450
Wait.

946
00:59:48,310 --> 00:59:51,210
Mr. Kwon actually has...

947
00:59:52,180 --> 00:59:53,220
a girlfriend.

948
00:59:56,320 --> 00:59:58,210
- What do you mean?
- Are... Are you serious?

949
00:59:58,990 --> 01:00:00,570
Mr. Kwon has a girlfriend?

950
01:00:00,860 --> 01:00:02,940
Yes, well...

951
01:00:04,730 --> 01:00:06,380
Well, it's...

952
01:00:10,130 --> 01:00:11,180
It's me.

953
01:00:17,670 --> 01:00:20,030
- You are so funny.
- Come on.

954
01:00:20,810 --> 01:00:22,880
- Seriously.
- That was great acting.

955
01:00:22,880 --> 01:00:24,880
She didn't even blink
when she made that joke.

956
01:00:24,880 --> 01:00:26,700
"It's me." Gosh, I don't think I can do it.

957
01:00:27,250 --> 01:00:28,330
I'm serious.

958
01:00:34,720 --> 01:00:36,980
I was quite hesitant to tell you at first.

959
01:00:38,290 --> 01:00:41,400
But I really like and trust everyone here.

960
01:00:41,400 --> 01:00:42,880
So I want to be honest with you.

961
01:00:45,200 --> 01:00:48,840
Mr. Kwon and I...

962
01:00:49,500 --> 01:00:52,700
are really dating.

963
01:01:03,850 --> 01:01:06,620
I like Mr. Kwon...

964
01:01:06,620 --> 01:01:08,610
very much.

965
01:01:11,660 --> 01:01:12,840
Oh, I see.

966
01:01:19,700 --> 01:01:21,820
Sir, isn't that hot?

967
01:01:23,670 --> 01:01:24,720
Gosh, that's hot!

968
01:01:27,940 --> 01:01:28,990
Water...

969
01:01:31,250 --> 01:01:32,900
I'm crying because it's hot.

970
01:01:33,450 --> 01:01:34,720
- Are you sure?
- Yes, it's because it's hot.

971
01:01:34,720 --> 01:01:36,280
Are you sure it's not
because you're heartbroken?

972
01:01:36,280 --> 01:01:37,660
No, it's because my hand's burning.

973
01:01:38,420 --> 01:01:41,450
My hand is burning.
That's why I'm crying. My gosh.

974
01:01:43,020 --> 01:01:45,560
I sincerely congratulate you.
My gosh, that was hot.

975
01:01:46,390 --> 01:01:47,510
I need to go to the bathroom.

976
01:01:47,900 --> 01:01:49,140
Gosh, I'm so happy.

977
01:01:49,360 --> 01:01:50,890
Goodness, I need to go to the bathroom.

978
01:01:51,870 --> 01:01:54,020
You guys should congratulate them.
My goodness, seriously.

979
01:01:57,370 --> 01:01:58,420
Thank you.

980
01:01:59,710 --> 01:02:01,100
Congratulations, Yun Seo.

981
01:02:03,780 --> 01:02:05,830
I never knew that so many people...

982
01:02:06,050 --> 01:02:08,140
were dating in our firm.

983
01:02:08,650 --> 01:02:09,690
I know, right?

984
01:02:10,020 --> 01:02:13,560
I really didn't expect Mr. Kwon
and Yun Seo to date each other.

985
01:02:14,050 --> 01:02:16,410
They seem really different.

986
01:02:16,660 --> 01:02:19,360
But at the same time,
they look really good together.

987
01:02:19,430 --> 01:02:20,670
I think they make a great couple.

988
01:02:21,900 --> 01:02:23,920
My goodness, they're forsythia flowers.

989
01:02:25,100 --> 01:02:26,210
You're right.

990
01:02:26,630 --> 01:02:28,620
Forsythia flowers are my favorite.

991
01:02:28,940 --> 01:02:32,140
By any chance, do you know the
meaning of forsythia flowers?

992
01:02:32,470 --> 01:02:34,260
No, what is it?

993
01:02:39,980 --> 01:02:43,660
"My love is deeper than yours."

994
01:02:46,420 --> 01:02:47,460
I see.

995
01:02:53,330 --> 01:02:55,050
Hey, Ms. Yang.

996
01:02:56,800 --> 01:03:00,770
If you don't mind, would you
like to eat with me someday?

997
01:03:03,240 --> 01:03:04,350
Sure, let's do that.

998
01:03:18,450 --> 01:03:20,110
Why are we drinking all of a sudden?

999
01:03:21,120 --> 01:03:23,820
Because I want to celebrate this day.

1000
01:03:24,430 --> 01:03:26,750
Today was the first time
we ever told anyone...

1001
01:03:26,790 --> 01:03:28,380
about our relationship.

1002
01:03:30,800 --> 01:03:32,950
But are you really okay?

1003
01:03:33,570 --> 01:03:34,710
I'm worried that you're doing this for me.

1004
01:03:36,140 --> 01:03:39,140
Mr. Kwon, do you know...

1005
01:03:39,840 --> 01:03:42,310
what you say to me the most?

1006
01:03:43,980 --> 01:03:45,120
"Are you okay?"

1007
01:03:45,880 --> 01:03:47,900
"Are you really okay?"

1008
01:03:48,380 --> 01:03:50,100
You always ask me that.

1009
01:03:51,420 --> 01:03:53,980
But today, this is what
suddenly came to my mind.

1010
01:03:55,460 --> 01:03:57,880
"He always asks me if I'm okay."

1011
01:03:59,630 --> 01:04:01,480
"But I wonder if he's okay."

1012
01:04:03,030 --> 01:04:04,590
"He's always so worried about me."

1013
01:04:05,470 --> 01:04:08,470
"And I'm worried he might not
be taking care of himself."

1014
01:04:10,700 --> 01:04:14,450
If you're not okay, I'm not okay either.

1015
01:04:16,240 --> 01:04:17,590
Because how you feel...

1016
01:04:18,580 --> 01:04:20,470
directly affects how I feel.

1017
01:04:23,420 --> 01:04:24,600
And there's one more.

1018
01:04:25,150 --> 01:04:28,490
I had to meet you today because
I wanted to tell you this.

1019
01:04:29,290 --> 01:04:30,300
What is it?

1020
01:04:33,060 --> 01:04:36,700
About that kissing scene earlier...
We didn't actually kiss.

1021
01:04:37,230 --> 01:04:40,000
Okay, let's not talk about that anymore.

1022
01:04:40,000 --> 01:04:42,060
Don't try to avoid
